Food
Integrated UI
A tea brewed from coffee beans roasted by Enit. Its deep and pleasant aroma fills the entire room.
<color=#800000>Cancels the compulsory rest penalty.</color>
Beef Bread
Piping hot bread made by Arden. The crunchy bread holds juicy beef and vegetables inside.
Beef stew made by Arden. It's not clear what exactly is in it, but it tastes really good.
BeefStew
Normal
Delicious
Perfect
Clala's handmade donut. Its gentle sweetness makes you feel good all the way while eating.
<color=#800000>Eating the food grants additional stamina for a limited time.</color>
Clala's handmade donut. The rich chocolate fills your mouth with sweetness, making you feel as if your energy quickly returns.
<color=#800000>Eating the food increases stamina recovery speed for a limited time.</color>
Clala's handmade donut. Packed with ground walnuts and nuts, one bite fills your mouth with a rich nutty aroma.
<color=#800000>Eating the food reduces stamina consumption for a limited time.</color>
A tea brewed from tea leaves dried by Rubrum. Refreshing for a light sip, with a clean finish that feels carefully prepared.
<color=#800000>Drinking the tea increases the appearance rate of special common gathering materials for a limited time.</color>
A tea brewed from tea leaves dried by Rubrum. Its warm and cozy aroma calms the mind, bringing comfort and a sense of heightened focus.
<color=#800000>Drinking the tea increases the appearance rate of special common gathering materials for a limited number of times.</color>
Clala's handmade donut. The strong aroma of walnuts and peanuts has earned it fame among children.
<color=#800000>Temporarily increases Ritoring's Gifts you obtain.</color>
Clala's handmade donut. It contains a slip of paper with auspicious words on it.
<color=#800000>Helps you detect Ritorings when you pass by one.</color>
Arden's steak. Juice pours from this perfectly cooked slice of meat when you bite down. The doneness depends on Arden's mood.
<color=#800000>Restores a random amount of Fatigue.</color>
Arden's handmade meat bun, consisting of a resilient sheet of dough wrapped around a meat filling, tender and al dente.
<color=#800000>Temporarily increases Fatigue recovery of all food.</color>
Arden's meat kebab. The aroma of fat sends strength flowing across your limbs.
<color=#800000>Partially restores the reduced capacity of recoverable Fatigue.</color>
Arden's spicy rib stew. Slightly spicy meat cuts in rich meat soup, this dish keeps you energetic throughout the day.
<color=#800000>Temporarily reduces Fatigue consumption.</color>
Restores Fatigue capacity
Recovers Fatigue randomly
Increases Fatigue recovery
Reduces Fatigue consumption
Grants extra Energy
Speeds up Energy recovery
Reduces Energy consumption
