This game collects anonymized game data to provide better service and a stable gameplay experience.
We ask for your consent regarding this.
Examples of collected information: player’s country, platform type, and game play logs (such as creature gathering, shop usage history, and quest progress)
-Data is stored locally on your device and will only be transmitted to the server if you press the “Agree” button.
-The data is anonymized, and sensitive personal information such as name, email, or contact details is not collected.
-The data is used to improve game quality, ensure stability, and guide future updates.
-The data is used only for statistical and improvement purposes and is not shared with third parties.
Providing consent is optional, and you can still play the game without any issues even if you do not agree.
You can also change your choice at any time in the game settings.
Agreeing to data collection helps improve the game service.
